author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Findel Says ‍Online Ordering Levels During Q3 Averaged 72%
text:
Jan 25 (Reuters) - Findel Plc:
* ‍YEAR TO DATE PRODUCT SALES HAVE GROWN BY 11.0% IN LINE WITH PLANS​
* ‍ONLINE ORDERING LEVELS DURING Q3 AVERAGED 72%, UP FROM 65% IN PREVIOUS YEAR​
* ‍NET DEBT ENDED DECEMBER 2017 AT £76.7M​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
